  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tAfter&nbsp;the long and cold winter, spring is <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/definitely\" target=\"_blank\">definitely</a> a season of new beginning. Fresh buds <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bloom\" target=\"_blank\">bloom</a>, animals awaken and the earth seems to come to life again. For us, it's better to remember and let&nbsp;the past moments&nbsp;go&nbsp;because spring's sunshine,&nbsp;breeze and&nbsp;shower always bring new hope for our future.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t- What does spring mean for you?</p>\n<p>\n\t- For these spring quotes below (or not list here), which one is your favourite？ Why？</p>\n<p>\n\tIt's spring fever. That is what the name of it is. And when you've got it, you want - oh, you don't quite know what it is you do want, but it just fairly makes your heart ache, you want it so! - Mark Twain</p>\n<p>\n\tLife stands before me like an eternal spring with new and brilliant clothes. - Carl Friedrich Gauss</p>\n<p>\n\tSpring is nature's way of saying, &quot;Let's party!&quot; - Robin Williams</p>\n<p>\n\tBehold, my friends, the spring is come; the earth has gladly received the embraces of the sun, and we shall soon see the results of their love! - Sitting Bull</p>\n<p>\n\tO, wind, if winter comes, can spring be far behind? - Percy Bysshe Shelley</p>\n<p>\n\tIn the spring, at the end of the day, you should smell like dirt. - Margaret Atwood</p>\n<p>\n\tSpring is God's way of saying, 'One more time!' - Robert Orben</p>\n<p>\n\tSweet spring, full of sweet days and roses, a box where sweets compacted lie. - George Herbert</p>\n<p>\n\tAutumn arrives in early morning, but spring at the close of a winter day. -Elizabeth Bowen</p>\n<p>\n\tSweet April showers do spring May flowers. - Thomas Tusser</p>\n<p>\n\t- DIY topic about spring season.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe spring season is full of transformation. The temperature rises to a more bearable degree, opposing Mother Nature's last few months of freezing surroundings. The leaves we saw fall and flowers we saw <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/wilt\" target=\"_blank\">wilt</a> are now budding into <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/lush\" target=\"_blank\">lush</a>, green <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/picture-perfect\" target=\"_blank\">picture-perfect</a> plants. Aside from the weather's transformation that occur in the spring season, we are transforming our lives too.</p>\n<p>\n\tWhen spring unfolds into our lives, we start to pick up the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/slack\" target=\"_blank\">slack</a> that winter instilled inside us of becoming laziness. The new year's resolution to join the gym starts being enforced, so you're sure to have your <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/abdominal\" target=\"_blank\">abdominal</a> muscles show in time for your beach vacation. No more lounging on the couch all day surfing the Internet - in the spring you can gather friends together at the park for your own game.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/891687/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p><br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p608609/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p608609\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p609145/\">2014年度职业排行榜：十大热门工作抢先看</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p609148/\">世界上最幸运的人：七次擦身死神后中大奖</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p609079/\">趣摄影：过去100年少女都打扮成什么样？ </a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p609232/\">再忙也得运动：如何将锻炼融入日常生活</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p609215/\">《催眠大师》莫文蔚翻唱 You Must Love Me</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p609525/\">2014福布斯中国名人榜：范冰冰蝉联第一</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p609498/\">英国大学反作弊海报写满公式 竟成免费小抄</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p605608/\">《生活大爆炸》谢耳朵教会我们的20件事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p609532/\">奥巴马出席白宫记者协会晚宴 变身“段子王”</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http:/